item.description:
in this collection we have form read, create and update API's

We need to Have these API's to show the categories in the SB forms and other places.

Read API:

``` json
{
    "request": {
        "type": "workspace",
        "subType": "categories",
        "action": "get", 
        "rootOrgId": "0138934136407244800" // Channel id
    }
}

 ```

We need to pass the root ord id (channel id) to get the category objects

Create / Update API:

In this we add properties and all the other validation similar as we add for SB forms

